      <h1 class='title'>Housing (Northern Ireland) Order 1983 (S.I. 1983/1118 (N.I. 15))</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='grand-committee-report-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HL Deb 17 May 2004 vol 661 c330GC</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_330gc' title='Col. 330GC &mdash; HL Deb 17 May 2004 vol 661 c330GC' name='column_330gc' href='#column_330gc' rel='bookmark'>330GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-04230'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_841' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        26 In Article 36(1)(d) (rent not to be increased on account of tenant's improvements), after "former spouse" insert "civil partner, former civil partner,".
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-04231'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_842' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        27 (1) Amend Article 47 (extended discretion of court in possession claims) as follows.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-04232'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_843' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        (2) In paragraph (5), for "tenant's spouse or former spouse, having matrimonial home rights" substitute "tenant's spouse or former spouse, or civil partner or former civil partner, having home rights".
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-04233'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_844' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        (3) In paragraph (6)&#x2014;
        <ol>
        <li>(a) after "the spouse or former spouse" insert ", or the civil partner or former civil partner", and</li>
        <li>(b) for "those matrimonial home rights" substitute "those home rights".</li></ol>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-04234'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_845' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        (4) In paragraph (7)&#x2014;
        <ol>
        <li>(a) in sub-paragraph (b), for "former spouse of the tenant" substitute "former spouse or former civil partner of the tenant",</li>
        <li>(b) in sub-paragraph (c), after "former spouse" insert "former civil partner".</li></ol>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0661P0-04235'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0661P0_20040517_GCR_846' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        (5) In paragraph (8) after "former spouse," insert "former civil partner,".
      </p>
      <ol class='xoxo'>
        
      </ol>
      
